 The organizers will recruit 200 patients in the study "To lower glucose levels and reduce weight by exclusion of carbohydrates and inclusion of psychological behavioral support" (LOWinCHIP) at the primary care health center "Cithyhalsan Centrum" in Norrkoping.

 Each patient will be followed for 2 years.

